@startuml
skinparam linetype ortho

title The Chord (The 512-bit Mono-Type)

class "AVX-512 Register" as ChordType << (C) Mono-Type >> {
    .. Geometric Structure (The Physics) ..
    + Bits 0-255 : GF(257) Prime Field
    .. Control Plane (The Engine) ..
    + Bit 256 : The 257th Bit (Parity Flag)
    .. Meta / Routing (The Map) ..
    + Bits 257-511 : Affine Constants & Guard Band
}

note left of ChordType::"Bits 0-255"
  <b>HALT Condition 2: Saturation</b>
  When ActiveCount hits the Shannon Ceiling.
  Applying rotation returns the exact same state.
  (Maximum Entropy Horizon).
end note

note right of ChordType::"Bit 256"
  <b>HALT Condition 1: The Trap</b>
  Hardware-level JNZ (Jump if Not Zero).
  Flipped explicitly when a boundary resolves.
end note

note right of ChordType::"Bits 257-511"
  <b>The Trajectory</b>
  Stores (a, b) for f(x) = ax + b.
  Defines where the particle is going next.
end note

@enduml